pageContext.claim: “Remember, the Republicans are 5-0 in Congressional races this year. In Senate, I said Roy M would lose in Alabama and supported Big Luther Strange - and Roy lost. Virginia candidate was not a "Trumper," and he lost. Good Republican candidates will win BIG!”
pageContext.analysis: Republicans are 6-1 in congressional races and the margin of victory was much lower than expected in many cases. Trump endorsed Luther Strange in Alabama, who lost, Ed Gillespie in Virginia, who lost, and then Roy Moore, who also lost.
